<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>圍村食桌 · 圍頭話保育</title>
    <!-- Font Awesome 6 (免費) -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Google 字體 -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            background-color: #FDF8F0;  /* 米白/奶油底色 */
            color: #3E3A36;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1300px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 40px;
        }

        /* 導航 (極簡) */
        .navbar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(253, 248, 240, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            z-index: 100;
            padding: 16px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196, 90, 50, 0.15);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .logo a {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #C45A32;
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #3E3A36;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover,
        .nav-links a.active {
            color: #C45A32;
            border-bottom-color: #C45A32;
        }

        /* 行動呼籲按鈕 */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #C45A32;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 12px 32px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.2s, transform 0.1s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(196, 90, 50, 0.3);
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #a84828;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .btn-small {
            padding: 8px 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        /* 首屏 Hero */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            min-height: 600px;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601050690597-df0568f7095c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop') center/cover no-repeat;
            /*  unsplash 盆菜風格圖片  */
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 900px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .scroll-down {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: white;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);}
            40% {transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-20px);}
            60% {transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-10px);}
        }

        /* 引言區 */
        .intro-section {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 100px auto 80px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .intro-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #C45A32;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .intro-section .quote {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #5e5a56;
            border-left: 4px solid #C45A32;
            padding-left: 30px;
            text-align: left;
            background: rgba(196, 90, 50, 0.03);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .flavor-icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .flavor-icons i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #7A9E7E;
            background: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .flavor-icons i:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            color: #C45A32;
        }

        /* 分類卡片 (節慶/家常/小食) */
        .category-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 60px 0;
        }

        .category-card {
            position: relative;
            height: 280px;
            border-radius: 28px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 30px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .category-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }

        .category-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.4s;
        }

        .category-card:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .category-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.6), transparent);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            padding: 25px;
            color: white;
        }

        .category-overlay h3 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px black;
        }

        .category-overlay p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        /* 盆菜專區 */
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            color: #3E3A36;
            margin: 80px 0 40px;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .section-title:after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #C45A32;
        }

        .pun-choi-area {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 40px;
            background: #f7efe5;
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .pun-choi-layers {
            flex: 1.2;
            min-width: 280px;
        }

        .layer-diagram {
            background: #fff1e4;
            border-radius: 60px 60px 20px 20px;
            padding: 20px 20px 30px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 -5px 0 #c45a3230;
        }

        .layer-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 40px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .layer-item:hover {
            background: #C45A32;
            color: white;
            transform: translateX(8px);
        }

        .layer-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            background: #C45A32;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }

        .layer-name {
            font-weight: 500;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .layer-meaning {
            color: #7A9E7E;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .pun-choi-desc {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 260px;
        }

        .food-pronounce {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px #eee;
        }

        .sound-btn {
            background: #C45A32;
            color: white;
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .sound-btn:hover {
            background: #a84828;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        /* 茶果卡片牆 */
        .snack-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 50px 0;
        }

        .snack-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: 0.25s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .snack-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(196, 90, 50, 0.12);
        }

        .snack-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .snack-info {
            padding: 18px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .snack-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .snack-pronounce {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            color: #7A9E7E;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .small-sound {
            background: #f0e4d8;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #C45A32;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* 家常菜網格 */
        .daily-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .dish-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px #f0e4d8;
        }

        .dish-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .dish-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .dish-info h4 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .dish-tip {
            color: #7A9E7E;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .mini-sound {
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: #C45A32;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* 橫向滑動小食區 */
        .snack-scroll {
            overflow-x: auto;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px 0 30px;
            scrollbar-width: thin;
            scrollbar-color: #C45A32 #f7e2d4;
        }

        .snack-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar {
            height: 6px;
        }
        .snack-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #C45A32;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .scroll-item {
            flex: 0 0 240px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .scroll-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 130px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        /* 發音字典卡片牆 */
        .dict-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .dict-item {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 15px 8px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px #f0e0d0;
            transition: 0.15s;
        }

        .dict-item:hover {
            background: #C45A32;
            color: white;
        }

        .dict-item:hover .dict-pronounce {
            color: #ffe7d0;
        }

        .dict-pronounce {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #7A9E7E;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .dict-sound {
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* 食譜下載區 */
        .recipe-section {
            background: #fff9f2;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 50px;
            margin: 70px 0;
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 30%, rgba(196,90,50,0.03) 0%, transparent 30%);
        }

        .recipe-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .recipe-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 25px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .download-btn {
            background: #C45A32;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* 影片區 */
        .video-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .video-card {
            border-radius: 30px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #2d2a27;
            aspect-ratio: 16/9;
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .video-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            opacity: 0.7;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .video-card:hover img {
            opacity: 0.5;
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .play-icon {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px black;
        }

        /* 結尾 */
        .closing {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background: #3E3A36;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 60px 60px 0 0;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .closing h2 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            color: #FDF8F0;
        }

        .closing .btn {
            margin-top: 30px;
            background: #FDF8F0;
            color: #3E3A36;
        }

        /* toast 提示 (模擬發音回饋) */
        .toast-msg {
            visibility: hidden;
            min-width: 200px;
            background: #3E3A36;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            z-index: 200;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .toast-msg.show {
            visibility: visible;
            opacity: 1;
        }

        footer {
            background: #2d2a27;
            color: #aaa;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* 響應式 */
        @media (max-width: 1000px) {
            .category-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .daily-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .dict-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); }
            .recipe-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .video-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .navbar { padding: 12px 20px; }
            .nav-links { gap: 1rem; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; }
            .hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; }
            .daily-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .dict-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
            .container { padding: 0 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- 固定導航 -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="logo"><a href="#">圍村食桌</a></div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">圍頭話</a>
            <a href="#">圍村歷史</a>
            <a href="#">圍頭地圖</a>
            <a href="#" class="active">圍村美食</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 首屏 Hero -->
    <section class="hero" id="top">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>圍村食桌<br>舌尖上的宗族記憶</h1>
            <p>一盤盆菜，一籠茶果，一代人的手藝與味道</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-down"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
    </section>

    <div class="container">

        <!-- 引言區 -->
        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>艾草的苦，雞屎藤的清香</h2>
            <div class="quote">
                「這些味道，城市裡找不到。它們只藏在圍村的廚房裡，藏在阿婆的手藝裡，藏在幾百年來每一個祭祖、團圓、豐收的日子裡。」
            </div>
            <div class="flavor-icons">
                <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-drumstick-bite"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-mortar-pestle"></i>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 美食分類導航卡片 (節慶/家常/小食) -->
        <div class="category-grid">
            <div class="category-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1626197031507-c1700f09f7ad?q=80&w=1974&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="盆菜">
                <div class="category-overlay">
                    <h3>節慶之味</h3>
                    <p>祭祖·團圓·豐收 —— 宗族的日子</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="category-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581075411249-0d9c3d3d6b6f?q=80&w=1974&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="家常菜">
                <div class="category-overlay">
                    <h3>家常之味</h3>
                    <p>圍村人的一日三餐，田邊的日常</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="category-card">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601494531612-31bc67c02d98?q=80&w=1974&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="茶果">
                <div class="category-overlay">
                    <h3>小食之味</h3>
                    <p>田埂上的零嘴，阿婆的手工</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 節慶之味：盆菜專區 -->
        <h2 class="section-title">盆菜 · 七層團結</h2>
        <div class="pun-choi-area">
            <div class="pun-choi-layers">
                <div class="layer-diagram">
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="1">
                        <span class="layer-icon">1</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">蘿蔔、豬皮</span>
                        <span class="layer-meaning">吸收肉汁·根基</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="2">
                        <span class="layer-icon">2</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">枝竹、魷魚</span>
                        <span class="layer-meaning">口感層次</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="3">
                        <span class="layer-icon">3</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">炆豬肉</span>
                        <span class="layer-meaning">宗族共食</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="4">
                        <span class="layer-icon">4</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">冬菇</span>
                        <span class="layer-meaning">珍貴食材</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="5">
                        <span class="layer-icon">5</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">雞</span>
                        <span class="layer-meaning">祭祀吉祥</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="6">
                        <span class="layer-icon">6</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">蝦</span>
                        <span class="layer-meaning">海味代表</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="layer-item" data-layer="7">
                        <span class="layer-icon">7</span>
                        <span class="layer-name">鮑魚/蠔豉</span>
                        <span class="layer-meaning">豐盛之最</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pun-choi-desc">
                <div class="food-pronounce">
                    <div class="sound-btn" data-word="盆菜"><i class="fas fa-volume-up"></i></div>
                    <div><strong>圍頭話：</strong> bun1 coi3  <span style="color:#C45A32; margin-left:10px;">(點擊喇叭聆聽)</span></div>
                </div>
                <p style="margin:20px 0 10px;">📜 起源傳說：一說南宋少帝南逃，村民以僅存食材共煮一鍋；一說文天祥被追，村民以大木盆盛菜招待。</p>
                <p>🍚 何時吃：祠堂祭祖、新春團拜、嫁娶喜宴、太平清醮。</p>
